		{
			description: [
				"{image:modpack:textures/dead-king.png width:160 height:90 align:center}"
				"The Dead King was once a powerful necromancer. Now his body sits atop his throne, waiting with the eye it guards hidden away. Dark magic can bind this king's soul to a compass, leading you to his catacombs. Take care of yourself and your surroundings, and this lord of the dead will fall before you."
				"PS: Don't think you've won after killing him once. The dead always come back."
			]
			id: "1D1BDE3EC94B4722"
			shape: "none"
			subtitle: "The Lord of Death"
