		{
			description: [
				"{image:modpack:textures/void-blossom.png width:160 height:90 align:center}"
				"The Void Blossom is an interesting thing. It's less monster and more plant. Reminds me of the old Tremorzilla films, but we're getting off topic. This flower is said to be found at the bottom of the world in lush caves and jagged crystals. They say a special flower made from amethyst can lead you to these caverns."
				"PS: I say you keep your distance. Thorns aren't pretty up close."
				""
				"&lDifficulty: &2Medium&r&r"
			]
			id: "3CCA251B73C9B4C6"
			shape: "none"
			subtitle: "The Crystal Flower"
