		}
		{
			description: [
				"{image:modpack:textures/frostmaw.png width:160 height:90 align:center}"
				"Cold? Let me tell you about cold. The Frostmaw is a hulking beast of the snow. You'll likely find him sleeping in your travels, but be wary. Waking one can quickly spell out a forever frozen fate. That said, play your cards right, and you can take down the behemoth, making the Cold Eye it guards all but yours."
				"PS: You might be able to snag the Ice Crystal it holds in its sleep, provided you're confident in your stealth."
			]
			id: "1467F080230DFEEE"
			subtitle: "The Yeti"
			tasks: [{
				id: "0E229B3DFC71CD15"
				item: {
					Count: 1
					id: "endrem:cold_eye"
					tag: {
						Damage: 0
					}
				}
				type: "item"
			}]
			x: 0.0d
			y: 3.0d
		}
		{
			description: [
				"{image:modpack:textures/umvuthi-throne.png width:160 height:90 align:center}"
				"Umvuthi, The Sunbird. I'll be frank with you, I don't like this guy. All these masks and cronies of his. But if you're in the savana, be sure to keep an eye out for an Umvuthana Grove. Maybe you have the strength it takes to slay this bird of terror and claim its Guardian Eye"
				"PS: Watch out for the laser."
			]
			id: "4FDACAE8F84DA3BD"
			subtitle: "The Sunbird"
