		{
			description: [
				"{image:modpack:textures/vizier.png width:160 height:90 align:center}"
				"Despite my love for the dark arts, I cannot say I am... pleased with the vizier. Though anybody wanting to learn more of the forbidden will inevitably come face to face with him. To call one as powerul &mand arrogant&r as him, one must make use of a scroll crafted with the illagers' prized totem. After that, it's only a matter of finding a dark manor, and &4you can tear his soul apart.&r"
				"Uh, excuse me, I got a bit sidetracked."
				"PS: Crowd control is your ally."
